<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">*والأقنى:</span> السائل الأنف المرتفع وسطه <span class="c2">(١)</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">*والأشّم:</span> الطويل قصبة الأنف <span class="c2">(٢)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">*والأدعج:</span> الشديد سواد الحدقة <span class="c2">(٣)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">*والضليع:</span> الواسع <span class="c2">(٤)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">*والشّنب:</span> رونق الأسنان وماؤها <span class="c2">(٥)</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">*والفلج:</span> فرق بين الثنايا <span class="c2">(٦)</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">*والمسربة:</span> خيط‍ الشعر الذي بين الصدر والسرة <span class="c2">(٧)</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">*وبادن:</span> ذو لحم <span class="c2">(٨)</span>.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">*ومتماسك:</span> معتدل الخلقة يمسك بعضه بعضا <span class="c2">(٩)</span>.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">*ومسيح:</span> لعلها بالسين المهملة وفتح الميم يعني عريض <span class="c2">(١٠)</span>.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">*الكراديس:</span> رؤس العظام <span class="c2">(١١)</span>.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">*شثن الكفين والقدمين:</span> لحمهما <span class="c2">(١٢)</span>.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
